cat << EOF
 Kgpg's kicker applet is a simple icon that integrates into your kicker. Then, you can drop files on it to encrypt/decrypt/sign/verify.
 A mouse right-click on it will bring a menu allowing encryption/decryption of the clipboard, to manage keys & more.
 GnuPG has never been so easy!

